data.title: Book of List - 2017
data.meta_description: Book of List_2017 - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. This document provides an overview and table of contents for the Puerto Rico Market Facts publication. The publication contains vital statistics and information on thousands of companies across over 120 industries in Puerto Rico. It includes rankings of industries, lists of the highest-paying occupations, incentives available, and profiles of the top 400 locally owned companies in Puerto Rico.
